---
import BaseLayout from "../layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.jsx";
import FooterReact from "../components/FooterReact.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="About YoutubersIncome.com"
  pageDescription="Learn what YoutubersIncome.com is, why it was created, and how it helps you estimate YouTube channel earnings based on views and CPM."
  pageUrl="https://youtubersincome.com/about"
>
  <Header />
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About YoutubersIncome.com</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      YoutubersIncome.com is a free tool that estimates how much money YouTube
      channels make based on public data like subscriber count, views, and
      average CPM (Cost Per 1,000 views).
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      Whether you're a fan curious about your favorite creator, or a YouTuber
      planning your strategy, our platform helps you get a realistic idea of
      potential ad earnings.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Why This Site Exists</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
      Millions of people search daily to know “How much does this YouTuber
      earn?” — but answers are often confusing or clickbait. We built this tool
      to provide quick, honest, and data-driven insights.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg space-y-2">
      <li>Make YouTube income estimation fast and transparent</li>
      <li>Help creators understand CPM and monetization potential</li>
      <li>Provide free tools and guides to grow YouTube channels</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Who Built This?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg">
      This site is built and maintained by a solo indie developer passionate
      about content creation and education. It's not affiliated with YouTube or
      Google — just made to help creators like you.
    </p>
  </section>
  <FooterReact />
</BaseLayout>
